---
import Blockquote from "../components/Blockquote.astro";
---

<div class="columns" id="introduction">
  <div class="column left">
    <img
      src="/markgodi_com/slowbuilt-book-promo-manual-edit2.png"
      alt="Book cover image for Slowbuilt: Education, Growth, and Grace (January 2026)"
      class="book-image"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="column right">
    <hgroup>
      <h2>Slowbuilt</h2>
      <p>Education, Growth, and Grace</p>
    </hgroup>

    <p class="data">Release date: January 2026</p>
    <p class="data">ISBN: 9798263584757</p>

    <p>
      <strong>Slowbuilt: Education, Growth, and Grace (January 2026)</strong> is the
      book I wish someone had handed me the day I walked into a classroom. Part memoir,
      part field guide, it’s everything school never taught us about becoming who
      we were meant to be for students, for teachers, and for leaders.
    </p>

    <p>
      Slowbuilt is not a book about being smart, gifted, or getting ahead. It’s
      about what happens when school, success, and identity quietly miss a large
      group of thoughtful, capable people. Blending lived classroom experience,
      personal reflection, and clear psychological insight, Slowbuilt explores
      how curiosity gets buried, why so many students and adults feel “behind”
      despite doing everything right, and what growth actually looks like when
      it isn’t fast, flashy, or rewarded on time.
    </p>
    <p>
      This book doesn’t promise shortcuts. It offers something rarer: language
      for what you’ve felt but couldn’t name, and a steadier, more humane way
      forward.
    </p>

    <ul class="links">
      <li>
        <a
          class="yellow"
          target="_blank"
          href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=slowbuilt+book&crid=SSCAZA8ZACBI&sprefix=%2Caps%2C190&ref=nb_sb_ss_recent_2_0_recent"
          >Order on Amazon
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a target="_blank" class="yellow" href="mailto:mark@markgodi.com"
          >Signed Copy/Contact me</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .columns {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-block: 3rem 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 120ch) {
    .columns {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .columns > .column {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .left {
    max-width: 35rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .left {
      max-width: 25rem;
    }
  }

  .left p {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .column {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    fit-content: cover;
  }

  img {
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-block-end: 1rem;
  }

  hgroup {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    hgroup {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  hgroup h2 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block: 0 1.25rem;
    color: #244057;
  }

  hgroup p {
    font-family: "EB Garamond", serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
    color: #244057;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .data {
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .data + .data {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .links {
      flex-direction: row;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  .links a {
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0.02rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 500;
    min-width: 20rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    margin-top: 0rem;
    color: #244057;
    background-color: #ebc975;
  }
  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .links a {
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      min-width: 15rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  .links a:hover {
    background-color: #244057;
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
</style>
